# AuraDoc 📄✨

**Upload a document. Ask questions. Get precise answers.**

AuraDoc is a Streamlit-based AI document Q&A app. Upload any PDF, start a chat, and ask questions — the app uses Groq's LLaMA 3.1 model to answer based strictly on your document's content. All chats are persisted in MongoDB so you can pick up where you left off.

---

## Features

- 🔐 **User authentication** — register and login with hashed passwords (bcrypt)
- 📎 **PDF upload** — extracts text from any PDF using pdfplumber
- 💬 **Persistent chat history** — all conversations saved in MongoDB per user
- 🤖 **AI answers** — powered by Groq API (LLaMA 3.1 8B Instant)
- 🗑️ **Chat management** — open, switch, and delete past chats from the sidebar
- 🐳 **Docker support** — run the full stack with a single command

---

## Tech Stack

| Layer | Tech |
|---|---|
| Frontend | Streamlit |
| AI / LLM | Groq API — `llama-3.1-8b-instant` |
| Database | MongoDB |
| PDF parsing | pdfplumber |
| Auth | bcrypt |
| Containerization | Docker + Docker Compose |

